snippet.title: RAW: US stealth B-2 bombers deployed to UK, land at RAF Fairford airbase

localized.description:
The US Air Force has sent more of its bombers to Europe, deploying two B-2 stealth aircraft as part of a military exercise. On Sunday they joined three B-52 StratoFortress bombers already deployed in Britain - READ MORE http://on.rt.com/isacgn

Courtesy: Ben Ramsay http://www.youtube.com/user/sonicbenj78/
